creator: Buzzrun apps
descriptionHtml:
Brick Blast is a classic and relaxing brick game. All you need to do is to aim, shoot and blast as many bricks as possible! While some levels can be a bit tough. Don’t worry, we have prepared you with various cool boosters and surprise gifts to help you easily wipe out all bricks.



What’s more impressive, you can even play with your friends! Now join our brick world and share the most exciting moments with your friends in Brick Blast!

* Tons of unique levels. All Free!

* Join a team for free lives, coins and cheerful team chat.

* Daily events, level chest and star chest to get a lot of rewards.

* Different game modes, different fun.

* Play without internet.



Never will you feel dull in this easy to play brick game with different game modes. Hurry to download and enjoy endless fun!



If you have any questions or suggestions on our game, feel free to contact us at feedback.
